buyerAgent.name: Shelly Salas Your Home Sold Guaranteed

data.description:
Introducing a fantastic new listing in the sought-after Bunny Trail community! This spacious home boasts 5 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, providing ample space for your family's needs. Additionally, one of the bedrooms can easily double as a home office, perfect for remote work or study.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by high ceilings that lend an open and airy feel to the home. The wood-like laminate flooring adds a touch of warmth and elegance, making you feel right at home. But the charm doesn't stop there; step into the backyard and discover a cozy fireplace area, perfect for relaxing evenings with family and friends.

Convenience is key with this property. Located just minutes away from Walmart, Fort Cavazos, and Texas A&M, you'll have easy access to shopping, entertainment, and educational institutions. Plus, it's zoned for Chaparral High School, the newest high school in the area, ensuring a quality education for your family.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a visit today and experience the comfort, style, and convenience this property has to offer. Your dream home awaits in the Bunny Trail community!
